[[div style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, .8);"]]
The Private Bureau of Investigation (PBI) is an American private military group formed out of the remaining members of the Federal Investigation Bureau. The PBI acts as a private intelligence agency and criminal investigative body that offers service to the highest bidder. 

The PBI has several permanent contracts with the ATLYS Corporation, being called into action whenever an ATLYS agent is KIA. They are also responsible for domestic surveillance and counterterrorism, acting as ATLYS’ primary special forces operatives when dealing with civilian matters. 
[[/div]]

